{"calories":"850","carbs":117,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eYou loved this pasta so much, we’re bringing it back as a repeat recipe this week. “Alla Norma” is a style of pasta sauce native to the Italian island of Sicily. Slow-roasted eggplant is folded into a cherry tomato sauce with onion, garlic, and basil. It’s tossed with corkscrew-shaped \u003cem\u003ecavatappi\u003c/em\u003e noodles, ideal for scooping up every saucy bite. And since no pasta would be complete without a little cheese, a creamy whipped ricotta is dolloped overtop.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eOne of our easy, family-friendly recipes for summer","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"75b4067707","fat":31,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50014/large_cropped_CnBOSgcCRrYFFGJe9cPH_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0008___MAIN.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50018/uzOZlrQWQWKBmVuGiBJK_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0008___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50018/hero_uzOZlrQWQWKBmVuGiBJK_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0008___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50018/menu_small_uzOZlrQWQWKBmVuGiBJK_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0008___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50018/small_square_uzOZlrQWQWKBmVuGiBJK_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0008___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50018/medium_square_uzOZlrQWQWKBmVuGiBJK_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0008___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50018/recipe_profile_page_uzOZlrQWQWKBmVuGiBJK_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0008___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50016/bfMrI1H3SRSE4Mt1l9pa_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0011___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50016/menu_small_bfMrI1H3SRSE4Mt1l9pa_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0011___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50017/odUUc0hIQ42n7kBbtFQ7_Cavatappi_alla_Norma_with_Whipped_Ricotta-0010___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}}],"name":"Cavatappi alla Norma with Whipped Ricotta","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"20-30","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":32,"public_slug":"4p-rigatoni-alla-norma-with-whipped-ricotta","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/32311/recipe_card20180629-12-1arvvca.pdf","recipe_id":5115,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Cavatappi alla Norma","subtitle":"with Whipped Ricotta","title":"Cavatappi alla Norma","legal_copy_short":"One of our easy, family-friendly recipes for summer","available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you\u0026#x27;ll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eAfter the sauce simmers in the oven, the pan will be extremely hot. Be extra careful, and use potholders or oven mitts when handling.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile it cooks, the pasta releases starches into the boiling water. Adding some reserved pasta water to the sauce will help it cling to the noodles. It’s easiest to reserve this water in a liquid measuring cup, if you have one.\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["8\" medium pot","baking sheet","10\" medium high-sided ovenproof pan"],"id":5115,"ingredients":["eggplant","cherry tomatoes","yellow onion","garlic","crushed red pepper","tomato purée ","cavatappi","ricotta cheese","basil","parchment paper"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"eggplant","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1366/medium_square_Eggplant.jpg"},{"name":"cherry tomatoes","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"pint","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/6/medium_square_cherry-tomatoes-test.jpg"},{"name":"yellow onion","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/27/medium_square_yellow-onion-test.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"crushed red pepper","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/39/medium_square_CRUSHED_RED_PEPPER_copy.jpg"},{"name":"tomato purée ","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2372/medium_square_medium_square_medium_square_ingredients-9.jpg"},{"name":"cavatappi","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2357/medium_square_2018-05-24___DS_18279079.jpg"},{"name":"ricotta cheese","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1486/medium_square_RICOTTA_CHEESE_-4386_copy.jpg"},{"name":"basil","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1276/medium_square_medium_square_basil-test.jpg"},{"name":"parchment paper","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/203/medium_square_paper-parchment.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50019/recipe_card_size_AXVj4BHRQpy5Lg8NlQ42_1._Prepare_Ingredients_2X_3X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Bring a medium pot of water to a boil over high heat. Rinse all produce. Halve \u003cstrong\u003eeggplant\u003c/strong\u003e lengthwise; thinly slice crosswise into .25-inch half-moons, discarding ends. Halve \u003cstrong\u003echerry\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e, halve, and thinly slice. Using the flat side of a knife, gently crush \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ecloves\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast eggplant","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50022/recipe_card_size_7jd3uDGQ5GQPJvr5QFoA_2._Roast_Eggplant.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eLine a baking sheet with \u003cstrong\u003eparchment paper\u003c/strong\u003e. Toss \u003cstrong\u003eeggplant\u003c/strong\u003e with \u003cstrong\u003e1.5 tablespoons olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eblack pepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Arrange in a single layer and roast until browned and very tender, 13-15 minutes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make cherry tomato sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50021/recipe_card_size_O0sYLhn5T4qONK20TNZU_3._Make_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile eggplant roasts, heat \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e in a medium high-sided ovenproof pan over medium-high heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003eonion \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003egarlic \u003c/strong\u003eand sauté, stirring, until beginning to soften, 3-4 minutes. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003ecrushed red pepper \u003c/strong\u003e(skip or use half for less heat), \u003cstrong\u003etomato purée\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003echerry tomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e. Transfer to oven and cook until sauce is thickened, about 10 minutes. Carefully remove from oven and set aside (see recipe tip).\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Boil cavatappi","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50023/recipe_card_size_aQG3u7ySjuGY94rS6jfu_4._Boil_Cavatappi.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile sauce cooks, season boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003ecavatappi\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until al dente, about 7 minutes. Reserve \u003cstrong\u003e.5 cup pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e, then drain and set aside (see recipe tip).\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Whip ricotta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50020/recipe_card_size_2._Make_Whipped_Ricotta.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile pasta cooks, in a small bowl, whisk together \u003cstrong\u003ericotta\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003e2 teaspoons olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e until light and fluffy—this is a great task for a kitchen helper. Season with \u003cstrong\u003ea\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003epinch of salt \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003eblack pepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Roughly tear or chop \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e leaves, discarding stems. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Finish and plate cavatappi","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/50015/recipe_card_size_roIk5M2BTe254C0ifwQw_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eRemove and discard \u003cstrong\u003ecrushed garlic \u003c/strong\u003efrom pan with sauce and return to medium heat. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003eroasted eggplant\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ecavatappi\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003cstrong\u003e half of basil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eblack pepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Add \u003cstrong\u003ereserved pasta water\u003c/strong\u003e, 1 tablespoon at a time, until sauce is silky and clings to noodles. Divide \u003cstrong\u003ecavatappi alla Norma\u003c/strong\u003e between serving bowls and top with \u003cstrong\u003ewhipped ricotta\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining basil\u003c/strong\u003e. Dig in! \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"fast + fun","slug":"fast + fun","hex_color":"#6FC0B1"},{"name":"Family-friendly","slug":"family-friendly","hex_color":""},{"name":"Quick cook","slug":"quick cook","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"fast + fun","slug":"fast + fun","hex_color":"#6FC0B1"},{"name":"Family-friendly","slug":"family-friendly","hex_color":""},{"name":"Quick cook","slug":"quick cook","hex_color":""}],"feature":[{"name":"fast + fun","slug":"fast + fun","hex_color":"#6FC0B1"}]}}